summary: Adds a pair of boots enchanted with resistance to all elements
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a pair of cloth boots (to be used by mages) that give the player resistance to all elements: Fire, Frost, Shock. The boots are located at the Arcanaeum, inbetween a bench and bookshelf (see screenshot).

To install the file, just download the zip folder, move the contents to your Skyrim Data folder, and activate it on your mod manager.
author: lumi135
